name: NotePal
overview:
NotePal is an online marketplace where users can buy and sell notes from events, such as conferences, seminars, speeches, class lectures, and more.

Users can browse, search for, and purchase notes generated by other users who have attended events and have created and uploaded the notes for sale on NotePal.com

In any given lecture event, there are hundreds, even thousands, of people who can’t attend because of scheduling conflicts, concurrent conference tracks, illness, lack of funds, or other reasons.

NotePal offers a simple and convenient way for people around the world or around the block to buy and sell notes from events such as conferences, seminars, class lectures and more.

NotePal will launch in private-beta in January 2010.
